name: Set of 3 Blue and Green themed childrens mini prints
description:
Decorate any little ones room easily and quickly with our gorgeous set of three mini prints.
These prints are resized from three of our popular prints - the turtle stack, our giraffe love and elephant ABC posters.
You will receive:

-Set of 3 prints.
-These are digitally printed on 300gsm satin finish card.
-Wrapped in a protective bag for posting and delivered in a sturdy mailer to protect them
-Size is 178mm x 128mm (each).

These will fit into standard 5x7 gap frames or just pop them straight onto the wall with washi tape, a peg or similar.
These make lovely presents or for your own home.

Any questions let me know!

name: Monkey boy Printable New Baby Poster
description:
Check out our range of birth announcement printable posters now available! Printable designs are customisable to your new baby and his or her details. You will receive a PDF or jpeg file customised to your requirements. From there you can print your poster yourself on your home printer or take it to a local print shop or photo kiosk
Our designs are all created in-house especially for your new arrival.

The cost to purchase includes one proof and your final file. Files can be sized either 8 x10" (20 x 25cm) or 5x7" (13x18cm). 

The process: Purchase this printable. Either include at checkout the details we need from you or you can email us at loveideasnz@gmail.com with the details. 

Let us know:
Your baby's name and weight, date of birth and city of birth.
If you want a pdf or jpeg file (if you are not sure just ask!)
If you want 8x10" or 5x7" (if you are not sure just ask!)

We will then email you a proof file within 1-2 working days (Monday - Friday NZ time). Please proof the file and return it to us as soon as you can with any changes. We will make the changes and send you a final file.

Please note you will receive a digital file only, there is no physical product with this order.

Any questions just contact us!
